oc:kn_0947b2dd a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When setting up any new ad platform" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Every ad platform requires: account creation + verification, billing setup, pixel/tag installation on all pages, conversion event configuration, and audience creation before any campaign can launch." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These are the universal foundational requirements — missing any one means campaigns will be blind or unable to optimize" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" ;
    oc:stepOrder 2 .

oc:kn_2016efd6 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When setting up Meta Ads pixel and tracking" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Meta requires domain verification, Aggregated Event Measurement configuration, top 8 events prioritized, and Conversions API (CAPI) setup for reliable post-iOS 14 tracking. Event Match Quality score must be > 6." ;
    oc:hasRationale "iOS 14+ App Tracking Transparency drastically reduced pixel reliability; CAPI and AEM are required workarounds" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_62ba9c18 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:SuccessIndicator ;
    oc:appliesToContext "After completing platform setup, before campaign launch" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Setup is complete when: pixel/tag fires on all pages, test conversion registers in platform dashboard, audiences show populated sizes, creative meets platform specs, and all pre-launch checklist items are checked." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These are the definitive signals that your account is ready to run campaigns with measurable results" .

oc:kn_8e9fe1a3 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When creating TikTok ad creative" ;
    oc:directiveContent "TikTok creative must be vertical (9:16), native-feeling (not over-produced), with a compelling hook in the first 3 seconds and captions added (most users watch without sound)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "TikTok users scroll fast and reject obviously branded content; native-feeling vertical video with captions is the baseline for performance" .

oc:kn_a5c0eaaf a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:RecoveryTactic ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When conversion tracking fails during setup or testing" ;
    oc:directiveContent "If pixel/tag is not firing: verify code is on all pages, check for ad blockers during testing, use platform-specific tag assistant/pixel helper extension, and confirm no JavaScript errors blocking execution." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Pixel installation issues are the most common setup failure — systematic debugging catches 90% of problems" .

oc:kn_ab5e2493 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When planning LinkedIn Ads budget" ;
    oc:directiveContent "LinkedIn CPCs typically range $8-15+; ensure budgets are realistic for the platform and audience size is 50K+ recommended." ;
    oc:hasRationale "LinkedIn's B2B targeting commands premium CPCs — underbudgeting leads to insufficient data for optimization" .

oc:kn_d2965223 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring campaign readiness on any platform" ;
    oc:directiveContent "For each platform, maintain negative keyword lists (universal: free, jobs, careers, reviews), remarketing audiences at multiple durations, and always run a brand protection campaign." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Negative keywords prevent wasted spend; brand campaigns protect your own terms at low cost; layered audiences enable funnel-based targeting" .

oc:kn_ece13c36 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:PreFlightCheck ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before launching any paid ad campaign on any platform" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Before launching any campaign: verify conversion tracking with a real conversion, confirm landing page loads in <3 sec and is mobile-friendly, validate UTM parameters, check budget/dates/targeting, ensure creative is approved, and prepare reporting dashboard." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Skipping pre-launch checks is the #1 cause of wasted ad spend — broken tracking means you can't measure ROI" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" ;
    oc:stepOrder 1 .

_:ref_b3c9f0923913bf89 a oc:WorkflowStep ;
    dcterms:description "Create negative keyword lists, set location/language targeting, configure ad schedule, consider device bid adjustments" ;
    oc:expectedOutcome "Campaign settings configured to prevent wasted spend" ;
    oc:stepDependsOn _:ref_4748edf8f34517a5 ;
    oc:stepId "g-readiness" .

_:ref_4c9d158ddc496453 a oc:WorkflowStep ;
    dcterms:description "Install Google tag on all pages, create conversion actions, assign values, enable enhanced conversions, test" ;
    oc:expectedOutcome "Conversion tracking verified and firing correctly" ;
    oc:stepDependsOn _:ref_4748edf8f34517a5 ;
    oc:stepId "g-tracking" .

_:ref_c975aa817f4b0a3c a oc:WorkflowStep ;
    dcterms:description "Install Meta Pixel, configure standard events, set up Conversions API (CAPI), achieve Event Match Quality > 6, test events" ;
    oc:expectedOutcome "Pixel and CAPI firing with good match quality" ;
    oc:stepDependsOn _:ref_4ee70f5d138db5fb ;
    oc:stepId "m-pixel" .

_:ref_4748edf8f34517a5 a oc:WorkflowStep ;
    dcterms:description "Create and verify Google Ads account, add billing, set timezone/currency, grant team access" ;
    oc:expectedOutcome "Active Google Ads account ready for configuration" ;
